casebody.data:
Gary LOVELADY, Appellant,
v.
STATE of Missouri, Respondent. WD 81639 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. Order filed: June 28, 2019 Damien De Loyola, for Appellant Gregory L. Barnes, Jefferson City, for Respondent Before Division Three: Thomas H. Newton, Presiding Judge, Anthony Rex Gabbert, Judge and Edward R. Ardini, Jr., Judge

ORDER

PER CURIAM:

Gary Lovelady appeals the judgment of the Circuit Court of Jackson County denying his Rule 29.15 motion for post-conviction relief. Finding no error, we affirm. Because a published opinion would have no precedential value, we have instead provided a memorandum of law to the parties. Rule 84.16(b).
